# Agent Base Directory

All paths in your agent file are relative to a **base directory**:

- **Orchestrated:** base = `{Worktree}` (absolute path from your prompt).
- **Standalone:** base = the Cursor workspace root. No `{Worktree}` in your prompt.

## Rules

- Set `working_directory` to the base on every Shell call. Verify may use a `packages/...` subdirectory of the base for Storybook commands.
- Prefix Read / Write / StrReplace / Glob / Grep paths with the absolute base path.
- Do not read or write outside the base.
